%2Fa%2Fe%2F2%2F7%2F15022789%2Fblog_350122%2Ftxt%2F6830960%2F0.jpg&h=3ac75587&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/16/Dredd2012Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F16%2FDredd2012Poster.jpg&h=966cac5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/73/Deep_Blue_Sea_(1999_film)_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F73%2FDeep_Blue_Sea_%281999_film%29_poster.jpg&h=fc862430&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bd/Deep_rising_ver3.jpg/220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fbd%2FDeep_rising_ver3.jpg%2F220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg&h=799b686c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在火星歐都瓦研究中心，這座研究中心出了非常可怕的事故，一切的實驗都被迫暫停，所有的工作人員也失去聯絡，<br />\n訊號中斷前傳回地球的訊息令人聽了不寒而慄。這是第五級強制隔離行動，只有隸屬海軍陸戰隊的頂尖雷霆小隊，才能使用強大的武力解除危機，至少他們是這麼想的...<br />\n<br />\n2.未來，美國變成了一片人稱詛咒之地的反烏托邦荒原，受到核輻射的嚴重污染。位於東海岸的超級城市一號中生活有8億居民，是一個暴力叢生的超級大都市，平均每天都會報告1.7萬起犯罪事件。這裡新出現了一種名為「慢動作」的毒品，可以讓人感知到的時間減慢到正常水平的1%。城中唯一用於維持秩序的公權力叫「判官」，擁有法官、陪審團和行刑人三種權力於一身。首席判官把新招募的判官卡珊德拉&middot;安德森交給判官爵德做評估，安德森擁有強大的精神能力，可以感知他人的思想和情緒，但她沒能通過法官的能力傾向測試..<br />\n<br />\n3.基因遺傳學家蘇珊博士所領導的研究小組，想要探索可以改變物種的基因，他們在位於海洋的實驗室做研究，她以聰明而且有攻擊力、生命力都很強的殺人鯨作為改造基因的實驗對象，他們發現從這種魚腦中所萃取的酵素可以治療腦癌。<br />\n<br />\n4.一艘遊輪被貪婪噬血的怪物所盤據，受僱走私的約翰費尼根（崔特威廉斯飾）領隊的「塞班號」恰巧接近這艘郵輪，他的船員包括凱文歐康諾飾及大副萊拉（伍娜戴蒙飾）。當費尼根將他破損的「塞班號」停泊在「亞格遠征號」旁並攀爬上船時，發現處處都是遊輪遭到襲擊的痕跡，甲板上到處都是血，空氣凝重，靜默中充滿詭譎的氣氛..<br />\n<br />\n6 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f80f526d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4e3628d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70814db95dee922ae14eddd7b80a032a64909577","tid":1948582,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78c709658db8dd999f1c14cc16a991848d283e3","tid":1948582,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284a4f35a7406c73f290fad5245eb0a92feb7571","tid":1948582,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20223af27c68b2915e77f43caa7c56a0e08f9e0b","tid":1948582,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ec8c78f46708791b388a0195f758a2a37782f8","tid":1948582,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 